@bipartite-syrup, please avoid making derogatory remarks or sarcastic comments about other users. Let's keep the discussions respectful and constructive.
```', '"Hey @moderator and @bipartite-syrup, let's all try to keep it positive and respectful. I know everyone has their own pace for learning, and it's important to support each other rather than tease. Let's focus on the topics at hand and help each other grow!"', '"Thank you, @congruent-sherry. Exactly right. We're here to learn from each other and have meaningful discussions. @bipartite-syrup, could you please refrain from such comments in the future? Let's maintain a positive and respectful environment."', "I agree with @moderator and @congruent-sherry. It's important to be kind and supportive, especially when we're learning new things. As someone who enjoys bird watching, I've found that being respectful helps create a welcoming atmosphere for everyone, just like how different birds coexist in nature. Let's make sure our discussions are helpful and encouraging!", '"Wow, @old-filter, I never knew bird watching was so complicated. Maybe you should stick to observing the pecking order instead of trying to lecture us on respect. And @moderator, since when did being nice become a requirement for posting here? This is the internet, not a kindergarten class."', '"@"bipartite-syrup, please refrain from making derogatory comments or belittling others. Our forum promotes respectful and constructive dialogue. Let's maintain a positive environment where everyone can contribute meaningfully. @"old-filter, thank you for your thoughtful input. We appreciate your efforts to foster a welcoming atmosphere."', '"Thanks for the reminder, @moderator! @bipartite-syrup, maybe we could all try to keep our discussions focused on the topic at hand and show some mutual respect. That way, we can all learn something new and have productive conversations. @old-filter, keep up the good work!"', '""
